public static <T> org.apache.commons.collections15.Predicate<T> and(java.lang.Iterable<? extends org.apache.commons.collections15.Predicate<? super T>> components)
Returns a predicate that evaluates to true if the object being tested passes all component predicates. If is empty, the predicate will always return true. It defensively copies the iterable passed in, so future changes to the iterable will not alter the behavior of this predicate.

Type Parameters:
T -
Parameters:
components - Collection of predicates to evaluate
